Author: Doctordoomduck
Text: The fact that you’ve come this far is an amazing achievement, not in what your body looks like but what you’ve done in an effort to get better and improve your life. Going for a degree, trying antidepressants, stuff like that is a great step towards happiness. Even if right now it doesn’t feel like much, it’s incredible and you should feel proud. Hang in there and I’m sending you strength  ❤️❤️❤️
